BFN 

  [Text] In view of the deaths of Cyprian Ntaryamira, 
president of the Republic of Burundi; and Juvenal Habyarimana, 
president of the Republic of Rwanda, the Council of State has 
decreed an official period of mourning beginning at 0600 on 11 
April until 1800 on 13 April. During this period, the Cuban flag 
will be flown at half mast in public buildings and military 
facilities. 

